<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>scellrun — scRNA markers report</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; max-width: 980px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; color: #222; line-height: 1.55; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: .3rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #444; }
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: .3rem 0 1.2rem; font-size: .9rem; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: .3rem .5rem; text-align: right; }
  th:first-child, td:first-child, th:nth-child(2), td:nth-child(2) { text-align: left; }
  thead { background: #f6f6f6; }
  .kv { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr; gap: .25rem .8rem; margin: .5rem 0 1rem; }
  .kv dt { color: #666; }
  .rationale { background: #fafaf6; border-left: 3px solid #c7b07a; padding: .6rem .9rem; margin: .6rem 0; font-size: .92rem; }
  .rationale strong { color: #5a4710; }
  footer { color: #888; font-size: .82rem; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: .7rem; }
  code { background: #f0f0f0; padding: .05rem .3rem; border-radius: 3px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>scRNA-seq cluster markers report</h1>

<h2>Summary</h2>
<dl class="kv">
  <dt>Cells used</dt>           <dd>{{ "{:,}".format(result.n_cells_used) }}</dd>
  <dt>Resolutions</dt>          <dd>{{ result.resolutions | join(", ") }}</dd>
  <dt>Test</dt>                 <dd>Wilcoxon rank-sum</dd>
  <dt>logfc_threshold</dt>      <dd>{{ result.logfc_threshold }}</dd>
  <dt>pct_min</dt>              <dd>{{ result.pct_min }}</dd>
  <dt>only_positive</dt>        <dd>{{ result.only_positive }}</dd>
  <dt>Top N per cluster (table)</dt><dd>{{ result.top_n }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Markers found per resolution</h2>
<dl class="kv">
{% for res, n in result.n_markers_per_resolution.items() %}
  <dt>res = {{ res }} ({{ result.cluster_counts[res] }} clusters)</dt>
  <dd>{{ "{:,}".format(n) }} marker rows
    — full list: <code>{{ csv_filenames[res] }}</code></dd>
{% endfor %}
</dl>

<div class="rationale">
  <strong>Defaults</strong>: Wilcoxon rank-sum, logfc ≥ 1.0, expressed in ≥ 25% of cells in
  the cluster, only positive markers. Same defaults the in-house pipeline uses; tune via
  <code>--logfc-threshold</code>, <code>--pct-min</code>, and <code>--only-positive/--all-direction</code>.
</div>

{% for res, top_html in per_res_top_html.items() %}
<h2>Top markers — resolution {{ res }}</h2>
{{ top_html | safe }}
{% endfor %}

<h2>Next step</h2>
<p>
  Open the per-resolution CSV alongside this report. v0.4 <code>scellrun scrna annotate</code>
  will match these markers against profile-specific panels (e.g. the Fan 2024 chondrocyte panel
  in the <code>joint-disease</code> profile) to produce two-tier celltype labels.
</p>

<footer>
  Generated by scellrun. Wilcoxon defaults match the in-house Liu lab pipeline.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
